restlib

Class ResponseBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • restlib.ResponseBuilder

  • @NotThreadSafe
public final class ResponseBuilder
extends Object
    A builder for generating Response instances. ResponseBuilder instances can be reused; it is safe to call build() multiple times to build multiple Response instances.
